Hi-Fi News - Yearbook 2014  UK

172 Pages | True PDF | English | 20 MB 

The ultimate guide for serious audiophiles, is globally renowned as the international top-end audio magazine. It contains the best in high end equipment reviews and views.  The oldest hi-fi magazine in the world is still delivering the best mix of international show reports, in-depth investigative features, world-class reviews, vintage celebrations and surely the most comprehensive range of music features available anywhere. And we're still the only magazine that tests high resolution music downloads.
